{"name":"Miracle: Lay on Hands","permission":{"default":0,"hsFJxrWN4M5Ezw3L":3},"type":"feature","data":{"description":"","req":"","source":"cfeature","category":"Cleric","benefit":"You can learn and use miracles, which are exceptionally potent greater powers. After you use a miracle, you must take a long rest before you can use another. You automatically know the lay on hands miracle, and you can learn others depending on your deity.","notes":"","sources":{"rfeature":{"label":"Racial Feature","value":"rfeature"},"cfeature":{"label":"Class Feature","value":"cfeature"},"ifeature":{"label":"Item Property","value":"ifeature"},"feat":{"label":"Feat","value":"feat"},"prof":{"label":"Proficiency","value":"prof"},"other":{"label":"Other","value":"other"}}},"flags":[],"img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"_id":"tx40bOEPUeoQkgXG"}
{"name":"Spellbooks (In a Nutshell)","permission":{"default":0,"hsFJxrWN4M5Ezw3L":3},"type":"feature","data":{"description":"","req":"","source":"cfeature","category":"Wizard","benefit":"The spellbooks class feature is a long list of rules, but here’s the short version:\n\nYour spellbooks contain alternate selections of Arcane powers. Each spellbook costs 25 gp to make, and they all have to contain the same number and kind of Arcane powers, from the same sources. You can have a number of extra spellbooks (aside from the one you’re using) equal to your Intelligence modifier. When you take a short rest, pick the spellbook that has the powers you want to have available until your next rest.\n\nSuggestion: Create a duplicate of your character for each spellbook, so that each copy has the powers from that spellbook. This way, you don't have to keep checking whether your current spellbook has the right power in it.","notes":"","sources":{"rfeature":{"label":"Racial Feature","value":"rfeature"},"cfeature":{"label":"Class Feature","value":"cfeature"},"ifeature":{"label":"Item Feature","value":"ifeature"},"feat":{"label":"Feat","value":"feat"},"prof":{"label":"Proficiency","value":"prof"},"other":{"label":"Other","value":"other"}}},"flags":[],"img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"_id":"u9psYHuZ0iieMrvb"}
{"name":"Troubled Sleep","permission":{"default":0,"hsFJxrWN4M5Ezw3L":3},"type":"feature","data":{"description":"","req":"","source":"rfeature","category":"Hellbound","benefit":"You cannot sleep for more than two hours out of every four, unless you are rendered unconscious by injury, illness or intoxicating substances. You only need four hours of sleep to complete a long rest.","notes":"","sources":{"rfeature":{"label":"Racial Feature","value":"rfeature"},"cfeature":{"label":"Class Feature","value":"cfeature"},"ifeature":{"label":"Item Property","value":"ifeature"},"feat":{"label":"Feat","value":"feat"},"prof":{"label":"Proficiency","value":"prof"},"other":{"label":"Other","value":"other"}}},"flags":[],"img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"_id":"uheDzoqlBKpK0jyX"}
{"name":"Tinkering","permission":{"default":0,"hsFJxrWN4M5Ezw3L":3},"type":"feature","data":{"description":"","req":"","source":"cfeature","category":"Artificer","benefit":"You can quickly modify the enchantments on magical items, adapting them to better suit your and your allies’ needs. During a long rest, you may alter one magical weapon, implement, or suit of armor that you have identified, turning it into a different magical item of equal or lesser value. The base type of item must remain the same: a magical longsword can only be turned into a different kind of magical longsword and magical chainmail can only be turned into a different kind of magical chainmail, for example. A tinkered item keeps its original monetary value, even if its new enchantment would normally be worth less. You do not need to have the construct magical item feat to use tinkering.","notes":"","sources":{"rfeature":{"label":"Racial Feature","value":"rfeature"},"cfeature":{"label":"Class Feature","value":"cfeature"},"ifeature":{"label":"Item Property","value":"ifeature"},"feat":{"label":"Feat","value":"feat"},"prof":{"label":"Proficiency","value":"prof"},"other":{"label":"Other","value":"other"}}},"flags":[],"img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"_id":"v8IuyTC6kMl2apIb"}
